<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>SHELL编程(learnLinuxTV) on 随记</title><link>https://lwmfjc.github.io/zh/docs/study/Linux/SHELLlearnLinuxTV_/</link><description>Recent content in SHELL编程(learnLinuxTV) on 随记</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 12:12:45 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://lwmfjc.github.io/zh/docs/study/Linux/SHELLlearnLinuxTV_/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>11-</title><link>https://lwmfjc.github.io/zh/docs/study/Linux/SHELLlearnLinuxTV_/11-/</link><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 12:12:45 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://lwmfjc.github.io/zh/docs/study/Linux/SHELLlearnLinuxTV_/11-/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="概念">
